            It moves on its own as if pulled by unseen hands.
            An old woman greats you at the dock.
            She tells you she will help you find the wizard if you can pass her tests''')

    
    choice = input("Do you go [accept] or [refuse]? ").lower()
    
    if "refuse" in choice:
        print('''\nThe old woman reveals herself as the wizard and attacks you!
        You pull out your sword and shield and move to defend yourself
